HTTP/1.0 403 Forbidden
Cache-Control: no-cache
Connection: close
Content-Type: text/html; charset=utf-8

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>403 Forbidden</title>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>403 Forbidden</h1>
  <p>This request has been blocked because our system recently detected an attack or malicious activity originating from your IP address.</p>
  <p>Access from your connection is temporarily restricted for security reasons. If you believe this is an error, please contact the service provider.</p>
</body>
</html>